### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

### Full refresh
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh

### Refresh events only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh/events

### Refresh venues only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh/venues

### Refresh tags/genres only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh/genres

### Refresh scores only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh/scores

### Ingestion logs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ingestion-logs

### Ranking
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ranking?genre=metal

### Dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dashboard/1?genre=metal

### City events
GET http://localhost:8000/api/cities/1/events?genre=metal


### Fast parallel refresh
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh

### Full slower refresh
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh?include_overpass=true&include_musicbrainz=true


### More complete Ticketmaster refresh with pagination and geo radius
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh/events?page_size=100&max_pages=10&days_ahead=365&radius_km=50&use_geo=true

### City-name only Ticketmaster refresh for comparison
POST http://localhost:8000/api/refresh/events?page_size=100&max_pages=10&days_ahead=365&use_geo=false
